name: Puri Agung Kerambitan
address: F33H+5XJ, Jl. Jurusan Kerambitan, Kerambitan, Kec. Kerambitan, Kabupaten Tabanan, Bali 82161, Indonesia
review 1: The place where the descendants of the Puri Kerambitan kings... beautiful and historical king's residential. Worth to visit and find out surprising secret behind each ceramic plates on the wall.
review 2: One best well preserved palace in Bali. It is unique due to the use of unearthed china founded when the palace was first built. This palace was home for 11 generation of kings of Tabanan.
review 3: Royal residence.  evocative and with a fascinating atmosphere and off the beaten track.
review 4: Last heritage and it is worthed to visit this palace.
